            <li class="prefix-icon guideline">Measure Summary</li>
            <li>NQMC:006401</li>
            <li>Jun 2009
            </li>            
                                </ul>
        <div>
                <h1>Pancreatic cancer: percentage of patients undergoing resection for whom the surgeon documents intraoperative findings in the operative note including the absence of 1) regional arterial involvement, 2) metastatic disease (liver, peritoneal, omental), and 3) distant adenopathy.</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /.content-header-meta -->

